      <div class="panel-body">
				<h4>This application is an original project created by myself. It was created to solve the problem of planning events with a large group of people without the need for long e-mail threads or group text messages.
				</h4>
				<h4>
				It is still a work in progress, but currently, some of things it is able to do are: create an event, invite individuals or people in the user created groups list, suggest locations from favorites, and suggest event times through drag and drop functionality.
				</h4>
				<h4>
				The app was created with Ruby on Rails for user authentication and the rest in Backbone.js. Other utilized technologies include RABL, jQuery, Bootstrap, and AJAX.
				</h4>
				<h4><a href="http://www.github.com/leesungchul/PlanItApp" type="button" class="btn btn-primary">Check Out the Code!!</a></h4>
				<h4><a href="http://planitapp.herokuapp.com" type="button" class="btn btn-primary">Check Out the Current Live Version!!</a></h4>
